    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >     世界被混乱与罪孽撕裂。踏足《罪域征途》的暗黑大陆，你将作为指挥官运筹帷幄，与原罪交易获得财富与力量，并通过棋盘对弈的方式前进，最终获得无上的权力与力量。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308960/extras/80ed24c12ae25d1785d0846bca9f3f0a.webp?t=1772445919\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308960/extras_big/80ed24c12ae25d1785d0846bca9f3f0a.webp?t=1772445919 width=1560 height=62 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308960/extras/d73fb2d272ae79eac8a9d5b52632f8ff.avif?t=1772445919\" width=1560 height=325 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308960/extras/50a5e3533657a6c5468b97ec8f30ee9c.poster.avif?t=1772445919\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308960/extras/50a5e3533657a6c5468b97ec8f30ee9c.webm?t=1772445919\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308960/extras/50a5e3533657a6c5468b97ec8f30ee9c.mp4?t=1772445919\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >     《罪域征途》的回合制棋盘战斗是步步为营的艺术。进入“指挥状态”的你需要精确地定位、旋转、移动和部署你的棋子，每一步都至关重要。您是选择稳扎稳打，还是兵行险着？算计好每一步，你的目标只有胜利。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308960/extras/80ed24c12ae25d1785d0846bca9f3f0a.webp?t=1772445919\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308960/extras_big/80ed24c12ae25d1785d0846bca9f3f0a.webp?t=1772445919 width=1560 height=62 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308960/extras/ce53fbc4c9748beab9ca8aff7c310d59.avif?t=1772445919\" width=1560 height=325 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308960/extras/e638a94619ab672f8f6085c6f232a231.poster.avif?t=1772445919\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308960/extras/e638a94619ab672f8f6085c6f232a231.webm?t=1772445919\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308960/extras/e638a94619ab672f8f6085c6f232a231.mp4?t=1772445919\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >     游历这个深陷黑暗的国度，独特的“罪孽系统”让你的每一个决策都举足轻重。您的每一步行动都会推动时间流逝，“威胁等级”亦会同步提升让敌人愈发致命，抉择也愈发沉重。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308960/extras/80ed24c12ae25d1785d0846bca9f3f0a.webp?t=1772445919\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308960/extras_big/80ed24c12ae25d1785d0846bca9f3f0a.webp?t=1772445919 width=1560 height=62 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308960/extras/fe107850ad0d648a8215e466039e41ed.avif?t=1772445919\" width=1560 height=325 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308960/extras/a07807071c325026558f5ee742833656.poster.avif?t=1772445919\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308960/extras/a07807071c325026558f5ee742833656.webm?t=1772445919\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308960/extras/a07807071c325026558f5ee742833656.mp4?t=1772445919\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >     从隐秘神龛到阳光大教堂，探索多样而危险的暗黑大陆。风险与挑战亦为财富和力量，直面强大的敌人，缔结盟友，在这个“善恶有报”的世界里留下你的足迹。你会为这片混乱带来秩序，还是投身黑暗吞噬一切？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308960/extras/c41d1c16ee8072f26498d907cf67e3e0.avif?t=1772445919\" width=1560 height=325 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308960/extras/b72d2a4b8ca4e3d25814026f5c09dd53.avif?t=1772445919\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308960/extras_big/b72d2a4b8ca4e3d25814026f5c09dd53.webp?t=1772445919 width=1560 height=162 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
